node.text:
Mayweather isn't just a boxer...he's a businessman. He's built a HUGE name for himself leading to an estimated $450M net worth(other networths have been reported for 2021).

His upfront fee for his fight against Paul was said to be $10M. Overall he reported he'll make between $50M and $100M.

This is the difference between him and many athletes...it takes a great businessman to be able to make big pay days like this.

Watch the ful video here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r4fcOyfVoLE&t=77s

Follow us @businessequity

node.text:
In 2000 Mark Cuban purchased the Dallas Mavs for $285M, as of 2021 the Mav’s value at $2.45B a 2% increase from last year.

Mark Cuban is worth $4.2B, is a host of Shark Tank, and is the owner of the Dallas Mavericks. He has transformed the fanbase and brand.

Follow us @businessequity

node.text:
CEO’s such as Zuckerberg and Musk are apart of the $1 per year “club”.

They choose to get paid $1 a year as a salary and pass off their savings in other ways.

Credit to: @johnefinance 
Follow us @businessequity

node.text:
@bastiaanslot_ has built a 7-figure consulting business from scratch in 2020, and is committed to showing others how they can do the same.

👉🏼Follow @bastiaanslot_
👉🏼Follow @bastiaanslot_
👉🏼Follow @bastiaanslot_ for the best business & consulting advice!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business Equity on August 19, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 7 principles that made me a millionaire in my early 20s. (A thread)'.

Photo by Business Equity on August 19, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot Goal setting. If you don't know what you want, then you don't know what to do. Set one clear, tangible goal. Achieve your goal, then repeat.'.

Photo by Business Equity on August 19, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 2. Sacrifice. If you don't sacrifice for what you want, then your goal becomes the sacrifice.'.

Photo by Business Equity on August 19, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 3. Health. Sleep wel Eat healthy. Meditate. Exercise. Take time to relax. If you aren't performing at your best, your business won't either.'.

Photo by Business Equity on August 19, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 4. Gratitude. Always looking to the future future can cause fear, anxiety, and stress. Practice gratitude daily to balance yourself.'.

Photo by Business Equity on August 19, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 5. Resist impulses. When you're working, resist all urges to eat snacks, grab a treat, or check social media. Train yourself to stay focused on the task at hand, and don't let anything distract you that's how you make progress.'.

Photo by Business Equity on August 19, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 6. Consistency. Whether you're seeing great results or no results at all, you need to stay consistent. Stay consistent without expecting immediate results. It will all add up long term.'.

Photo by Business Equity on August 19, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 7. Invest in yourself. etc. Whether it's books, mentors, seminars, Make sure you're constantly investing in your own growth. You don't have to figure out everything on your own. Find someone who has the results you want and learn from them. That's your "shortcut" to success.'.

Photo by Business Equity on August 19, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot Whenever you're feeling stuck or like you're not making progress in life life you can always go back to these principles and see where you're going wrong. |focus on these daily to make sure I stay on track'.

Photo by Business Equity on August 19, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot If you'd like to see more content and tips abon what learned from building a 7-figure consulting business, drop me a follow.'.

node.text:
Simon Cowell started his career in the music industry working in a mailroom and later became a talent scout for musicians, a small-time record producer and a consultant in the industry.

In the early 2000's he co-created the hit shows Pop Idol and American Idol, and today he's responsible for a few artisits who have made it to fame.

ANYONE can make it.

Follow us @businessequity

node.text:
In simple terms...buy assets first and use that cash flow to pay for your liabilities.

This is how the wealthy continue to build and maintain their wealth.

Credit to @mikeytaylor 
Follow us @businessequity

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business Equity on August 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says '$ Business Equity @businessequity Starbucks genius way to get millions of dollars in free marketing: They spell your name incorrectly It's not hard to spell Paul, but they'll still spel it "Pawl" so he can talk about it on social media Giving starbucks FREE advertising'.

node.text:
Some of these misspellings may be intentional and some may not be. Either way it's genius marketing.

Coca-cola did the same sort of thing when they sold bottles with names on them. People would post a picture of a bottle with their name on social media and boom free advertising.

Think outside the box!

Follow us @businessequity

node.text:
This life is meant for living the way you want, and if that means working a 9-5 there's nothing wrong with that.

The idea is to NEVER settle! If you want more get after it.

Follow us @businessequity

node.text:
If you want to set your kids up for success give them all the knowledge you never had.

Generational wealth is basically useless if you neglect the major part of passing down your newly learned knowledge.

Credit to: @johnefinance 
Follow us @businessequity
